===Etymology===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*rV-mi(k)|t=to sleep; to dream}} (STEDT under *r/s-mwəy). Cognate with {{cog|bo|རྨི་བ||to dream}}, {{cog|bo|རྨི་ལམ||dream}}.

